Package: ececplots
Type: Package
Title: Standardized Visualization Tools for ECEC and ECS Teams
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("ECEC/ECS Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Mauricio.SALAZAR-LOZADA@oecd.org")
Description: Provides standardized scatterplots and barplots for the
    ECEC and ECS teams with a consistent base frame that controls figure
    dimensions and panel layout. All plots share the same width and height
    dictionaries and load custom fonts from the package fonts directory.
    An Excel macro companion allows figures to be exported to Excel with
    the underlying data attached.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0),
    patchwork (>= 1.1.0),
    rlang (>= 1.0.0),
    showtext (>= 0.9),
    sysfonts (>= 0.8)
Suggests:
    openxlsx (>= 4.2.0),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
